Interface FormatPlugin

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AvroFormatPlugin, EasyFormatPlugin, ExcelFormatPlugin, HttpdLogFormatPlugin, ImageFormatPlugin, JSONFormatPlugin, LogFormatPlugin, LTSVFormatPlugin, MapRDBFormatPlugin, ParquetFormatPlugin, PcapFormatPlugin, PcapngFormatPlugin, SequenceFileFormatPlugin, ShpFormatPlugin, StreamsFormatPlugin, SyslogFormatPlugin, TableFormatPlugin, TextFormatPlugin

    public interface FormatPlugin
    Similar to a storage engine but built specifically to work within a FileSystem context.
